<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-08-30T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-08-30T15:00:00-05:00" n="1010" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1010">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">861.24/8–3044: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Harriman</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-08-30T23:00:00+03:00">August 30,
                                    1944—11 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received August 30—4:39 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>3231. ReDeptel 2066, August 29, 3 p.m. I have noted that the Department
                            has given Stepanov final terms on all points under discussion in
                            connection with Fourth Protocol financial proposal. I am so informing
                            Mikoyan in connection with a letter I am addressing to him on related
                            matters. The Department has been most cooperative and patient with the
                            Soviets in what must have been most exasperating negotiations and I hope
                            that as a matter of principle no further concessions will be made.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Harriman</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>